 15:38 MBOBMELA: Three people were transported to hosptial for minor injuries after an accident happened on the N4 at the gorge. ER24 operations manager Kim Habib said no serious injuries were reported at the scene and the three patients were taken to Mediclinic Nelspruit. TRAC N4  reported that the road has been cleared for traffic.  15:00 MBOMBELA :  TRACN4 reported that a collision at the gorge on the N4 has caused a pile-up of vehicles. Motorists are asked to remain patient while recovery is under way.  There is a stop-and-go set up. Lowvelder will update with more information as it becomes available. 